ed="T" n="0775b24"/><persName key="A010502">釋甄公</persName>，姓<name>魯</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000027764">江陵</placeName>人也。少而警慧，<date key="j19935311993895" from-iso="+0746-01-01" to-iso="+0746-12-31">七歲</date><lb
ed="T" n="0775b25"/>誦通《詩．雅》，遂應州舉，三上中第，未釋褐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1566"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0775b26"/>與沙門議論玄理，乃願披緇，投<placeName key="PL000000027757">福壽寺</placeName><persName key="A010503">辯<lb
ed="T" n="0775b27"/>初<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>，以為模範。後於<placeName key="PL000000023574">洛京昭成寺</placeName>講法<lb
ed="T" n="0775b28"/>數座，因<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz12"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz12"/><placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName>禪師，通暢心決。方至<placeName key="PL000000011072">丹陽<lb
ed="T" n="0775b29"/>茅山</placeName>，尋挂錫於<placeName key="PL000000009825">蘇州楞伽山</placeName>，四遠參玄者<pb ed="T" n="0775c" xml:id="T50.2061.0775c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0775c01"/><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz13"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>胼</sic><corr>駢</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz13"/>肩疊足矣。時<persName key="A004029">白樂天</persName>牧<ref type="place" target="#PL000000009928">是郡</ref><ptr target="#n1561"/>，接其談道，<lb
ed="T" n="0775c02"/>不覺披襟解帶，心遊無物之場，得<persName key="A010502">甄</persName>之閫<lb
ed="T" n="0775c03"/>閾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g641"/>矣。遂堅請出<placeName key="PL000000009885"><anchor xml:id="beg0775007"/>水流<anchor xml:id="end0775007"/>寺</placeName>，不樂安止，以山<lb
ed="T" n="0775c04"/>水為娛情之趣耳。<date from-iso="+0829-02-12" key="j20238892024242" to-iso="+0830-01-31"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz14"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz14"/>和</name>三年</date>，示疾，云終九<lb
ed="T" n="0775c05"/>十歲。以<date key="j20239932023993" when-iso="+0829-05-27">其年四月十七日</date>入塔焉。</p>
